<h1 class="search">{{title}}</h1>
<main>
  <p class="search">This is a web application to find marvel Characters. We are
    using Marvel api by signing up and using Public key and Privater Key. We
    will implement methods to search and show marvel characters fetched from
    marvel API. you can type your favourite character in box below!!!</p>
  <form action="/search" method="post" class="search">
    <label for="searchTerm" class="search">Enter Character to Find</label><br />
    <input type="text" name="searchTerm" id="character" class="search" /><br />
    <input type="submit" class="search" />
  </form>
</main>